      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/uk-s-biggest-investor-lgim-ditches-trump-trade-on-biden-drop-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法律与通用投资管理公司 (Legal &amp; General Investment Management) 放弃了对国债收益率曲线将变陡的押注，称总统乔·拜登退出美国大选降低了共和党横扫全场的机会。]]></description>
