      <title>联合利华股价因销量增长和盈利能力提高而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着联合利华首席执行官海因·舒马赫 (Hein Schumacher) 的扭转策略开始取得一些进展，该公司上半年销量增加、盈利能力提升，股价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行和美国银行表示挪威克朗跌势过猛，应买入该货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/socgen-bofa-say-time-to-buy-norway-s-krone-as-rout-is-overdone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威克朗已跌至一年多以来的最低点，货币策略师和投资者纷纷抓住这一机会，押注该货币将从底部附近反弹，跃升至十国集团 (G10) 的榜首。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/socgen-bofa-say-time-to-buy-norway-s-krone-as-rout-is-overdone</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
